<ab facs="#facs_157_r1l2">Biſchoff cʒü Meincʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_157_r1l3">Biſchoff cʒü wircʒpurg </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_157_r1l4">Lienharten Grafen vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
                        cʒü Caſtell </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_157_r1l5"><expan>Conrad<ex>en</ex></expan> Schencken herren cʒü
