<ab facs="#facs_157_r1l8"><expan>Dıetth<ex>er</ex>n</expan> landſchaden vicʒtum
                        cʒü Aſchaffemburg </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_157_r1l9"><expan>Arnolt<ex>en</ex></expan> von Seckendorff
                                <expan>Amptma<ex>n</ex></expan> cʒü der Newenſtat an der Eyſch </ab>
</div>
